First, use the 'vial' tool on any 'solid, mundane' ingredient (e.g., dandelion, mushroom, amber) to create a mundane extract. Second, use the 'vial' tool on any 'solid, magical' ingredient (e.g., unicorn horn, sunstone) to create a magical extract. Finally, combine these two extracts (mundane and magical) to achieve the maximum score of 100. Avoid the 'filter' tool as it generally lowers value. Also, be cautious about combining basic ingredients directly or using the 'vial' on gas/liquid items, as these often result in negative values or botched extractions. Focus on extracts from solids!
